    <id>journalnotes</id>
    <name>Journal</name>
    <summary>A Markdown journal and personal knowledge workspace for Nextcloud</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
Journal is a private Markdown journal and personal knowledge workspace for Nextcloud.

Features:
- Daily entries organized by date
- Native Markdown files stored in Nextcloud
- YAML Front Matter
- Multiple categories
- Nextcloud System Tags
- Full-text search across content, dates, categories, tags and wikilinks
- Nextcloud Text editor
- PDF and Markdown export
- English, Spanish and German translations

Your content remains accessible as regular Markdown files inside your Nextcloud storage.
]]></description>
